  <original-body>I don't know if it is a bug, but i had a small headache therefor ^^

@@@ ruby
class User &lt; ActiveRecord::Base  
   belongs_to :customer  
end  

class Customer &lt; ActiveRecord::Base  
   has_one :user

   delegate :name, :to =&gt; :user, :prefix =&gt; nil
end
@@@

works but

@@@ ruby
   delegate :name, :to =&gt; :user, :prefix =&gt; false
@@@

doesn't


Edit: I'm using Rails3 RC / Ruby 1.9.2-head</original-body>
